1
00:00:59,360 --> 00:01:00,240
Hello, Su Wan.

2
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:03,680
Hello.

3
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:04,599
Hello.

4
00:01:06,240 --> 00:01:08,560
Alright, I'll leave Bai Qing to you from now on.

5
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:09,890
You can go tutor her now.

6
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:13,560
But didn't we promise to...

7
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:18,160
Promise what?

8
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:20,480
Promise.

9
00:01:20,960 --> 00:01:23,680
We promised that for your entrance exam,

10
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:25,360
you'll rank in the top fifty.

11
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:33,640
Then I'll leave it to you, Ms. Su Wan.

12
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:34,800
It's fine.

13
00:01:34,960 --> 00:01:36,490
Let's do our best together.

14
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:37,920
Then, brother, we...

15
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:38,640
Go ahead.

16
00:01:38,800 --> 00:01:40,039
Okay, come with me.

17
00:01:51,080 --> 00:01:51,740
Take a seat.

18
00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:58,000
Sit down.

19
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,400
You like Tiansuan too?

20
00:02:12,920 --> 00:02:13,520
Yeah.

21
00:02:13,760 --> 00:02:14,920
When I was unhappy,

22
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:17,280
I got through it by listening to their songs.

23
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:18,540
I really like them too.

24
00:02:20,079 --> 00:02:22,810
At that time, the person and dog I cared about most

25
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,850
passed away one after another.

26
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:27,079
My mom became very controlling.

27
00:02:28,079 --> 00:02:30,200
When I felt the most suffocated,

28
00:02:32,200 --> 00:02:34,000
I got through it by relying on it.

29
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,320
At least you have a mom.

30
00:02:36,200 --> 00:02:37,460
I don't even have a mom.

31
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:44,920
You still have a dad and brothers who love you.

32
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,260
You are very lucky too.

33
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:48,240
By the way,

34
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:51,960
Between your eldest and second brother,

35
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,840
who are you closest to?

36
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:58,240
Are you dating my brother, Sister Su Wan?

37
00:03:00,760 --> 00:03:01,400
I...

38
00:03:03,640 --> 00:03:05,960
How about we start with math today?

39
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:08,360
I really don't understand geometry at all.

40
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,480
Sure.

41
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:15,560
What was your math score in the college entrance exam, Sister Su Wan?

42
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:18,200
That's amazing.

43
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:22,650
Dinner is ready. Come down and eat.

44
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:25,290
How about this, let's go eat first.

45
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:26,530
I'm a little hungry.

46
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,260
Dad, let's eat.

47
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:36,320
Okay.

48
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:38,680
Okay.

49
00:03:39,079 --> 00:03:39,720
I'll do it myself.

50
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:40,440
Sit tight.

51
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:41,280
Dad.

52
00:03:44,320 --> 00:03:45,120
Hello, Uncle.

53
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:47,360
She is Bai Qing's new tutor, Su Wan.

54
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:50,440
Hello, Ms. Su.

55
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:52,440
Have a seat.

56
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:57,040
Thank you for tutoring Bai Qing from now on.

57
00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:58,640
No problem.

58
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:00,600
Let's eat.

59
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:03,520
Here.

60
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,800
Help yourself.

61
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:15,840
I was afraid you'd be shy.

62
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,260
Make yourself at home.

63
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:18,120
No, I...

64
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:18,880
Su Wan.

65
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:21,480
There's no need to avoid my dad like this.

66
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,840
Who spoiled you like this?

67
00:04:22,840 --> 00:04:23,480
Yaqi.

68
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:43,880
Uncle, I'm really not, I...

69
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:45,120
It's okay.

70
00:04:45,400 --> 00:04:46,659
Is anyone in the store?

71
00:04:48,159 --> 00:04:49,360
I'll go. I'll go.

72
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:53,090
Dad, I'll go take a look too.

73
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,120
Okay.

74
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:02,440
You brat, what are you doing?

75
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:04,800
It's your first time meeting Ms. Su, and you're so impolite.

76
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:06,000
She was impolite too.

77
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,040
Hello.

78
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:13,840
Are you here to get your car fixed?

79
00:05:13,840 --> 00:05:14,320
Yes.

80
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:17,290
Please get mechanic Bai Tianyu for me.

81
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:18,720
I am Bai Tianyu.

82
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:25,040
You are a young mechanic.

83
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:28,180
This car drives smoothly,

84
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:29,320
but there are some strange noises.

85
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:31,180
I'm worried it's unsafe to drive.

86
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:32,840
I heard mechanic Bai Tianyu

87
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:35,440
is famous for fixing this kind of high-end car.

88
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:36,409
How about it?

89
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:39,100
Have you worked on this model before?

90
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:40,000
Wait a moment.

91
00:06:20,760 --> 00:06:22,220
It's a lubrication issue.

92
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:24,370
You haven't driven this car

93
00:06:24,400 --> 00:06:25,480
for at least half a year, right?

94
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:27,880
The lubricant in the engine and transmission

95
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:29,540
has dried up or deteriorated.

96
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:33,020
That's why it made abnormal noises when you drove it out today.

97
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:34,240
Not bad.

98
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:36,720
Mr. Bai, despite your young age,

99
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:38,960
you have such professional knowledge of cars.

100
00:06:38,960 --> 00:06:39,800
You are right.

101
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:42,400
I haven't driven this car for over half a year.

102
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:43,320
This car...

103
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,760
It's a gift I gave my son before.

104
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:49,560
He will graduate with his Ph.D. and return home this weekend.

105
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:51,960
So I want to drive this car to pick him up myself.

106
00:06:51,960 --> 00:06:53,400
It will be more meaningful that way.

107
00:06:53,400 --> 00:06:54,760
I took it out for a spin today

108
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:56,159
and found some problems.

109
00:06:56,440 --> 00:06:58,200
My driver went to a few garages,

110
00:06:58,880 --> 00:07:00,520
but they couldn't find the issue.

111
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:01,380
I didn't expect

112
00:07:01,760 --> 00:07:04,320
Mr. Bai to be so professional.

113
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:05,720
Thank you.

114
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:09,840
I'll leave the car to you to fix.

115
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:15,560
You can contact me directly if you need anything.

116
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:17,090
If you can finish it on time,

117
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:19,840
I guarantee all our company's future cars

118
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:23,060
will be given to you for maintenance and modification.

119
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:25,280
I'm trusting you then.

120
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:27,560
I'll leave this precious baby here.

121
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,320
Okay.

122
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:29,880
You can just leave the car here.

123
00:07:29,880 --> 00:07:30,200
Okay.

124
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:31,080
Come pick it up this weekend.

125
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:33,280
Hurry up and fix it. Don't delay my business.

126
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:33,880
Take care.

127
00:07:33,880 --> 00:07:34,560
Take care.

128
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,280
You're so amazing.

129
00:07:37,280 --> 00:07:38,940
You're practically a master.

130
00:07:40,760 --> 00:07:44,290
I told you there's definitely something wrong with this woman.

131
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:52,000
It should be this one.

132
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:56,440
The parts we talked about last time have arrived.

133
00:07:56,440 --> 00:07:58,440
You can come pick up the car tonight.

134
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:04,140
What are you doing?

135
00:08:05,520 --> 00:08:06,800
I can't find my screwdriver.

136
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:08,860
Can't I just come over and take a look?

137
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:13,040
Stay away from her. Go do what you need to do.

138
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:13,720
Fine.

139
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:16,800
So the crazies are sticking together, huh?

140
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:17,720
Boring.

141
00:08:17,840 --> 00:08:18,570
Are you okay?

142
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:20,720
Thank you.

143
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,000
Hey, Su Wan.

144
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:31,120
I've sent you the address.

145
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:33,000
For our Animal Behavioral Psychology class,

146
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,159
I applied for a make-up exam.

147
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:37,159
If you don't show up this time, I'll really beat you up.

148
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:38,200
No problem.

149
00:08:44,640 --> 00:08:45,970
What are you smiling at?

150
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:50,440
I need a huge favor. Take me somewhere.

151
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:51,040
Please.

152
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:53,890
Let's go.

153
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:01,000
Let me see.

154
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,040
Yaqi.

155
00:09:08,680 --> 00:09:09,740
What are you doing?

156
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:12,160
What's wrong with buying a few lottery tickets?

157
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:13,240
Just a few?

158
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:15,120
This could be worth five million. Give it back.

159
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:15,960
Are you dreaming

160
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,320
of getting rich overnight again?

161
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:20,380
Did you borrow money online again and can't pay it back?

162
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:24,040
Liu Yaqi.

163
00:09:24,040 --> 00:09:26,160
It's bad enough that you don't work hard.

164
00:09:26,160 --> 00:09:27,560
Can you be more sensible?

165
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:30,240
Did I ask you to pay it back this time?

166
00:09:30,760 --> 00:09:31,400
No.

167
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:33,610
So keep your mouth shut.

168
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:35,520
Come back to the factory with me now,

169
00:09:35,520 --> 00:09:36,780
or I'll tell Dad today.

170
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:37,500
Bai Tianyu.

171
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:40,450
Mind your own business.

172
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:54,760
We're here. It's just ahead.

173
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:58,400
Let's go.

174
00:10:00,280 --> 00:10:01,600
Where exactly are we going?

175
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:02,800
An animal shelter.

176
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,960
Animal shelter?

177
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:08,360
You go if you want.

178
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:10,280
I have no interest in cats and dogs.

179
00:10:10,280 --> 00:10:11,960
Come on, we're almost there.

180
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:12,800
Please.

181
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:19,680
Are you afraid of small animals?

182
00:10:21,280 --> 00:10:22,000
Me?

183
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:24,880
Fine, let's go.
